ADDITIONAL DISCLAIMER FOR VOLCANIC ERUPTION FORECASTING

This software is intended for research purposes only. The eruption forecast
model provides probabilistic predictions and is NOT GUARANTEED to predict every
future volcanic eruption. Volcanic systems are inherently complex and 
unpredictable.

This software is NOT GUARANTEED to be free of bugs or errors. Users should:
- Validate all results independently
- Use this tool as one component of comprehensive volcano monitoring
- NOT use this software as the sole basis for public safety decisions
- Always consult qualified volcanologists for expert interpretation
- Follow official warnings from local volcano observatories and government agencies

The authors and contributors accept no liability for any damages, losses, or
consequences arising from the use of this software for volcano monitoring,
eruption forecasting, or public safety decisions.